issue.body:
@prockenschaub, @matteogales, I wanted to bring to your attention the discussion in https://github.com/alan-turing-institute/sktime/issues/347 on datetime indices.

This concerns the sktime core interface for the forecasting module, but the data container (choice) as well.

In partiular, I'd be interested to hear your opinion on the question of how to treat the index of series/frames, and the [multi-input/output design linked there](https://github.com/alan-turing-institute/sktime/wiki/Design-proposal%3A-multi-type-input-output).
